873653776, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 74, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-07-02 11:21", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=873652992,45974302,8688]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=65610553]来一份甜辣的甜不辣[/uid] (2026-07-02 11:16):[/b]<br/><br/>半导体板块甚至都在-1以内了，都在抄底？[/quote]<br/>你看错了  只有材料在反弹。", "lou": 3565, "content_length": 29, "reply_to": 873652992, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1782962505}, {"pid": 873654979, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 102, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-07-02 11:29", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=873654455,45974302,8691]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=63173758]莫凡ruomoi[/uid] (2026-07-02 11:26):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大，可以问一下你最近都是满仓吗？我已经没有抄底资金了。[/quote]<br/>对  所以靠调仓解决问题。<br/>我的满仓是90%左右  留10%做日内T<br/>所以我今天肯定是亏的  但是亏损已经从地狱爬起来的那种[s:ac:哭笑]", "lou": 3566, "content_length": 104, "reply_to": 873654455, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1782962961}, {"pid": 873657485, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 44, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-07-02 11:46", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=873656600,45974302,8693]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=40830380]紫幻→星辰[/uid] (2026-07-02 11:39):[/b]<br/><br/>呜呜呜，原来满仓还要留10%。[/quote]<br/><br/>我一直都是这样的啊", "lou": 3567, "content_length": 23, "from_client": "8 Android", "reply_to": 873656600, "postdatetimestamp": 1782963970}, {"pid": 873661882, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 73, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-07-02 12:19", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=873657977,45974302,8694]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=64786164]XX的小迷弟[/uid] (2026-07-02 11:49):[/b]<br/><br/>对于我这种资金不如狼大0.01%的，留10%和不留没啥区别[/quote]<br/>这个跟我的技术策略有关<br/>如果一点不剩 在外围黑天鹅引起的大跌我就会没有参与感。没有参与感我就会弱化盘面敏感度。", "lou": 3568, "content_length": 111, "reply_to": 873657977, "from